ACCLAIMED singer Tom Baxter will play a one-off gig in Ayrshire. Tom to play Troon show ACCLAIMED singer Tom Baxter will play a one-off gig in Ayrshire.The songwriter will play South Beach Sessions in Troon on Thursday October 16.He is best known for his first single, Better, which featured in David Schwimmer's hit film Run Fat Boy Run.Tickets, priced &pound;12.50, are available from www.southbeach.co.uk or the South Beach Hotel. 